1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:28,000
 Dobrodošli u 55 minuta kod Željke Markić. Hvala da pratite moj YouTube kanal. Moja današnja gošća je misionarka Časna Dorotea Đunđer koja je već dugin iz godina djeluje u Beninu.

2
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:36,000
 Časna Dorotea, puno hvala da ste našli vremena na vašem godišnjem odmoru u Hrvatskoj za ovaj naš razgovor.

3
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:42,000
 Hvala vam lijepo na pozivu i drago mi je da mogu par minuta podijeliti s vama.

4
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:56,000
 Mi smo se dvije upoznale u Beninu, dakle kad smo ga mi posjetili radi marijnih obroka. Vi ste se u stvari kroz to smo se upoznale. Vi ste otvorili dvije škole, sada već i tri škole.

5
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
 Četvrta se sad otvara u Beninu, je li tako?

6
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
 Peta, peta.

7
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:23,700
 Da, da, dakle mi smo preko veličatnog odilona koji je došao u Hrvatsku. Nekako se Hrvatska, na njegove župi su se upoznali sa njim, dakle želeći uz vratit mu su otvorili prvu kuhinju marijnih obroka Hrvati iz Varaždina, su otvorili u Beninu i onda smo kroz to upoznali i vas.

8
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:33,000
 Viste danas koordinirate sve kuhinje marijnih obroka u Beninu koje otvara u stvari marijni obroci Hrvatska.

9
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:46,800
 Da, istina je. Prva kuhinja je otvorena preko veličasnog odilona, ali je bila jako vizana uz nas. Jer odilon je tu, jedini mi smo tamo koji bismo mogli to malo kao koordinirati.

10
00:01:47,000 --> 00:02:04,960
 A s vremenom druga sela vidjeći kuhinju i dobro koje se čini toj djeci u tom selu, u tom školi, pa su tražili isto takvu kuhinje za njih. Danas ima puno tih sela, škola koje traže kuhinje.

11
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:26,060
 Ali mi moramo ići postepeno, polanko, tako kako bi mogli na neki način to dobro organizirati. Jer puno je djece, puno ih dolazi u školu, a mi smo tamo već dugo, dugo, puno prije nego što je odilon upoznao Hrvatsku, mi smo bili u Beninu.

12
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:35,720
 Tako da, mi smo bili u Beninu, a Hrvatska u stvari nije nas puno poznavala. Hrvatska je upoznala Benin preko veličasnog odilona.

13
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:40,960
 To je na neki način, reći ćemo malo žalosno, ali dobro da je tako.

14
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:49,680
 Ali dobro da je tako, pa na neki način i naš veličasni odilon je plod tog svog zajedničkog djelovanja u crkvi.

15
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,300
 A sigurno.

16
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:57,840
 Tako i tog misionarskog rada i ljubavi koja se ulaže već desetljećima u Benin. Vi ste u Benin došli prije...

17
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:04,060
 Ja sam došla u Benin 88. godine. Znači 33 godine sam ja u Beninu.

18
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:11,300
 Meni je bilo tako simpatično ono kako smo putovali zajedno i išli na sjever Benina kako ste...

19
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:14,800
 Vi u stvari govorite, kad govorite o Hrvatskoj, govorite mi Hrvatskoj.

20
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,560
 Mi u Hrvatskoj.

21
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:18,380
 A onda kad se govori o Beninu, govorite mi u Beninu.

22
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:26,560
 Vidite, mi smo u Beninu i na neki način ja ću reći za sebe, ja sam srasla tamo u Beninu.

23
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,880
 Kad me netko pita, sest, odakle ste došli iz Benina?

24
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:34,700
 Uopće mi ne pada na pamet, da kažem, iz Zagreba ili iz Bosne.

25
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:42,440
 Ja sam Hrvatica, rođena sam u Žepču, imam kuću, moje sestre imaju u Zagrebu u Beninu.

26
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:46,460
 I jednom zgodom je da mi pozornio, sestra, kako je to rodit se u Beninu?

27
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:52,400
 Tek mi je onda sinulo u svijest, u stvari što sam rekla.

28
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,820
 Kažem ja pa lijepo.

29
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:57,740
 Neki se negdje rađaju, neki se rađaju i dva puta.

30
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:04,840
 A to je u stvari moj slučaj i baš lijepo se rodit u Beninu i rasti s Beninom.

31
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:15,800
 Jer kad ja pogledam sad unazad mojih tih 33 godine i onda vidim na neki način taj rast Benina i rast tog naroda.

32
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:20,600
 Makar da smo još uvijek jako, jako daleko od Evrope.

33
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:29,420
 Što kopiramo od Evrope ono što je negativno za nas tamo u Beninu i što nas pritišće više i doleg zemlje.

34
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:33,260
 A dobre stvari nekako idu teže.

35
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:43,500
 Tako da sa tim marinim obrocima mi u Beninu, reći ću, činimo jako puno dobroga za taj narod.

36
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:49,060
 Djeca dolaze u školu i škola završava u podne.

37
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:53,300
 Od podne do 3 sata djeca imaju pauz.

38
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:57,340
 U to vrijeme bi trebali otići kući, jest i vratit se.

39
00:04:57,340 --> 00:05:04,760
 Mnoga djeca su daleko, a mnogi od njih nemaju ništa u podne za jest.

40
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:09,660
 Tek kad se roditelji vrate iz polja, onda će djeca jest, ali to je na većej.

41
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:17,520
 Tako da mnoga djeca ostaju u školi, na putu, igraju se, ali bez obroka.

42
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:27,540
 Nakon da je taj obrok koji naše djeca dobiju u podne je veliko bogatstvo za školu, za narod.

43
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:35,280
 I onda se vidi u stvari velika promjena uspjeha djece koja imaju volju za učit, a nemaju mogućnosti.

44
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:42,160
 Svi mi znamo kako je teško nešto misliti ili raditi ako si gladan.

45
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:44,760
 Sad djeca ujutro šta su jela? Ništa.

46
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:56,180
 Oni su došli u školu i neki su donijeli 50 franaka, 100 rijetki koji će nešto pojesti.

47
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:58,820
 A 100 franaka vam nije ništa.

48
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:02,640
 Ti nemaš tu eto toliko da staviš dva zaloga je u usta.

49
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:05,920
 Jer kod nas je danas postala hrana jako skupa.

50
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:10,280
 I znači djeca su cijeli dan bez jela.

51
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:18,940
 I onda što se događa sad kad mi otvorimo školu u jednom, kuhinju u jednoj školi.

52
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:27,140
 Mnogi raditelji iz susjednog sela premještaju svoju djecu u tu školu samo da bi imali taj obrok.

53
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:29,700
 Jedan u danu, tu kašu koja...

54
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:36,940
 Jedan u danu, to je nije baš kaša, to je jedan prilično zahvalan obrok za njih.

55
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:39,200
 Jer za naša djeca jako puno jedu.

56
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,240
 Oni bi toga puno više pojeli da im se da.

57
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:50,320
 Ali mi pratimo te mjere koje su nam određene, koje ne možemo ići u beskonać.

58
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:55,460
 Ali evo recite, evo vi imate tjedni, dakle meni, dakle od ponedeljka do petka.

59
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:57,780
 Što je ono što se djeci osigura?

60
00:06:57,780 --> 00:07:04,800
 Tako programirano. Ja sam programirala tako da djeca jedu ponedeljkom rižu i dobiju jedno jaje.

61
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,460
 Svako djete dobije jedno jaje.

62
00:07:06,460 --> 00:07:14,980
 Utorkom djeca dobiju žgance, tu kukuruznu kašu sa nekakvim umakom od zelja i dobiju malo ribe.

63
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:18,320
 To su istina malo ribe, ali to je za začin više.

64
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:21,760
 Srijedom djeca dobiju grah.

65
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:30,940
 Uz grah imaju ili grah je uz kukuruzno brašno ili jedan puta dajemo im uz to brašno od manjoke.

66
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:35,060
 Inače se to kod nas, to je naše glavno jelo i uvijek je to.

67
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:41,660
 Onda četvrtkom ponovo imaju žgance uz umak od nekakvog zelja ili paradajza.

68
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,100
 Onda petkom imaju ponovo rižu.

69
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:51,540
 Vi ste mi nekada, i kad smo bili djeca, neka djeca su po prvi puta pojela jaje.

70
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:55,500
 Pa većina njih ne jedu oni jaje doma.

71
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,160
 To je luksuz.

72
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,440
 I ti nema ga.

73
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:02,120
 Međutim, neće vam nijedno djete jesti da to ne jede doma.

74
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,000
 Kad vi pitate djecu, reći će jedemo.

75
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,280
 Iako možda nisu nikad jeli.

76
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:10,920
 Jer u njih je taj osjećaj.

77
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:16,260
 Ako on kaže da nema ili da ne jede, znači on sam sebe ponižava.

78
00:08:16,260 --> 00:08:18,000
 A to oni ne želi.

79
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:21,180
 I onda makro da je gladan, neće ti reći da je gladan.

80
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:26,260
 Mene je ono baš oduševilo, više sam puta to vidjela u školama,

81
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:35,460
 kako neka djeca ostave dio hrane i nose kući u šalicama za svog mlađeg brata ili sestru koji ne ide u školu.

82
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:39,820
 Dakle, on sam se nije najao, ali nosi kući za svog mlađeg brata.

83
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:47,540
 Ima dosta djece koja ponesu od kuće nekakvu zdjelicu i onda tu hranu stave unutra, nešta će pojest.

84
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:49,880
 Ako idu u kući, onda će odnijet kuće.

85
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:53,240
 Neki će ostati tu, pa će onda to poslije pojest.

86
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:59,440
 Na kraju, jer od poodne do najveće šest sati je daleko.

87
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:03,720
 I onda on, sad ću pojest malo, pa ću poslije dodati malo.

88
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,120
 Ili pak nosi kući.

89
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:08,060
 Da, vi ste, kako ste vi došli u Beninu?

90
00:09:08,060 --> 00:09:14,720
 Kako ste vi došli u tu zemlju za koju kažete da vas raduje rast, da raste ona i da je vi uz nju isto ste raste?

91
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:26,520
 Vidite, u tu zemlju smo otišle na sed dvije, sam 18. godina, ali to vam je jedan poziv nutarnji koji je teško objasniti i praktički nemoguće.

92
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:29,680
 U nas pitaju zašto baš Benin? Ne znamo.

93
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:34,760
 Ali to nam je Benin bio zasađen nekako u srce i samo tamo.

94
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:39,820
 Mi smo išli u Benin jednostavno da pomažemo tom narodu.

95
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,420
 Oba dvije smo medicinske sestre.

96
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:43,820
 To mi je bio prvotni cilj.

97
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,920
 Njihovo zdravstvena zaštita, ranca, djecom i to.

98
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:49,420
 Istina, nismo mi puno znali.

99
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:52,540
 Ni potrebe Benina, ni mogućnosti.

100
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:59,740
 Ali vi ste kao časna redovnica u družbi se stara čudotvorne medaljice.

101
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:02,700
 Tamo željeli, osjetili se da bi željeli ići u misje?

102
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:09,420
 To je bio jedan poziv nutarnji koji praktički ja sam ga odbijala godinama, godinama i onda sam došla do kraja.

103
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,960
 Sad više, sad Norašić.

104
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,900
 To vam je...

105
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:15,360
 Odbijali, odbijali.

106
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,860
 Odbijali, na koncu si došao do zida.

107
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,400
 Sad više ne možeš dalje.

108
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:22,880
 A mislim da je tako sa mnogim pozivima kud?

109
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,000
 Ideš u nepoznatu.

110
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,420
 U stvari ne znaš uopće kud ideš.

111
00:10:25,420 --> 00:10:26,480
 Ni zašto ideš.

112
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,540
 Ali znaš da moraš ići.

113
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:30,580
 I tako smo nas dvije otišle.

114
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:32,160
 Poslali su nas.

115
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,780
 Dobili smo jednu kuću.

116
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:37,740
 Biskupija nam je napravila kuću u jednom selu koji se zove Afame.

117
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:42,120
 To je naša prvo selo i nama najdraže selo.

118
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,620
 U tom selu nije bilo ništa.

119
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:48,200
 Nismo imali ni vode, ni struje.

120
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,240
 Došli smo u praznu kuću.

121
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,680
 I onda poslije nešto nam je biskup dao.

122
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:54,240
 Nešto smo mi privrijedili.

123
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:57,080
 Ljudi su iz sela nam donosili vodu.

124
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:59,240
 Da ne idemo mi na rijeku.

125
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:02,400
 Voda je nije bila zdrava.

126
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,980
 Mi smo kupovali prvo vrijeme vodu za pit.

127
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:07,320
 Nas dvije pa toliko smo mogle.

128
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:12,280
 I onda polako u selu praktički nije bilo ništa.

129
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:15,320
 Ja sam bila jedina žena koja vozi.

130
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,740
 I možda za neki desetak godina.

131
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:22,040
 A osim toga na početku nije bilo možda 20 auta u cijelom Beninu.

132
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:26,760
 Pa meni su rekli da kad ste vi tamo došli da ste vi bili jedina žena koja vozi u Beninu.

133
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:28,760
 U Beninu. Jedina žena u Beninu.

134
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:33,320
 U cijelom Beninu sam ja bila jedina žena koja vozi.

135
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:36,380
 Dakle da ste vi bili prva bijelkinja koju su oni vidjeli.

136
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:37,540
 Bilo je bijelaca.

137
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:38,980
 Bijeli se stara tamo.

138
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:41,680
 Ali nitko od njih ne vozio.

139
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:44,980
 Jer većina se stara niti danas ne vozio.

140
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,080
 Oni imaju njihovog šofera.

141
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,780
 A mi vozimo.

142
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:52,780
 Nemamo toliko srestava da bi plaćali šofera.

143
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:54,680
 I popravke auta za njim.

144
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,580
 Jel ovako?

145
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,340
 Mi kad vozimo znamo kud idemo.

146
00:11:58,780 --> 00:11:59,600
 i kako vozimo.

147
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,860
 Ja vam moram reći.

148
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:03,140
 Vi ste tema naših razgovara i u obitelji.

149
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:05,680
 Mi kad smo bili prvi put u Beninu je bio moj suprok s nama.

150
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:07,780
 I putovali smo gore visoko na sjever.

151
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:08,940
 I vi ste vozili.

152
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:10,380
 Niste njemu dali da vozimo.

153
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:11,600
 Ja, ne, ne, ne.

154
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,400
 Ja ga ubijem sada oko toga.

155
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:17,200
 Evo sestra Dorotea ti nije dala mu voziti.

156
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:18,980
 Ali rekao da ste odlična vozačica.

157
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:24,380
 Čujte, neko strani vozi na nepoznatom putu.

158
00:12:24,380 --> 00:12:26,420
 Nikad ne znaš.

159
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:30,920
 Ja znam od prilike sve što bi se moglo na tom dogoditi.

160
00:12:31,180 --> 00:12:33,520
 Ne, ne, da, i to na putu vam je sve vidjeli ste.

161
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:36,460
 I koze, i djeca, i ovce.

162
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:38,040
 S tim je moraš računati.

163
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,120
 A još kakav je put.

164
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:43,220
 Ali vi ste, kako je to bilo kad ste vi došli iz Hrvatske,

165
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:46,180
 tamo u tu kuću, u sred Afrike.

166
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:47,640
 Kako je to bilo?

167
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,240
 Vi ste tada koliko godina ste imali?

168
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,460
 Sam tada imala 35 godina.

169
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:51,180
 35 godina.

170
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:55,700
 Ono, najljepši vrijeme, najljepši život.

171
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:56,900
 Bila sam u Zagrebu.

172
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:58,260
 Radila sam u bolnici.

173
00:12:58,260 --> 00:13:00,900
 I to vreme mi je bilo baš najljepše.

174
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:03,760
 Imaš ograničeno svoje radno vrijeme.

175
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:04,720
 Završiš posao.

176
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,940
 Ideš kući.

177
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:08,260
 Kod kuće imaš molitvu.

178
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,340
 I drugo, koliko stigneš pomoći drugima.

179
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:13,120
 Ali eto, meni je rečeno, baš sad.

180
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,680
 Izvoli, Doroteja, trebam te u Beninu.

181
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:16,480
 Baš sad.

182
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,580
 I mi smo došli tamo u sve to.

183
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:21,100
 Pa ne znam.

184
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,440
 To je, mislim, posebna Božja milost.

185
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:28,060
 Da mi nismo osjetili tu prazninu, niti nekakav nedostatak.

186
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:34,540
 Kad su nam drugi pričali, kako su oni iz početka imali averziju prema tome.

187
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:37,840
 Jedino, bilo mi je ono, strašno, sve je bilo prljavo.

188
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,060
 Prljavo, da, da.

189
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:40,600
 Sve je bilo prljavo.

190
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,640
 Mnogi nisu imali naviku čišćenja.

191
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,580
 Danas čistim, sutra će opet biti prljavo.

192
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:51,100
 I praktički, ređeću, mi smo počeli sa tim čišćenjem, uređivanjem.

193
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:54,380
 I ono me smetalo, to mi je išlo po glavi.

194
00:13:54,380 --> 00:13:56,640
 Svi koji su hodali, vukli su noge.

195
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:59,580
 Čuješ i na deset metara.

196
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,740
 Ja pa ne možete dignuti noge, po tako.

197
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:05,820
 Danas toga više već nema.

198
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:10,620
 Te dvije stvari i danas svi gledaju da to bude čisto.

199
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:12,420
 Oni će pomesti ispred svoje kuće.

200
00:14:12,420 --> 00:14:16,040
 Da, vidi ih se često ujutro, baš kako čiste ispred kuće.

201
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:17,900
 Da, no, oni čiste ispred kuće.

202
00:14:17,900 --> 00:14:20,960
 Ali to je posignuto na taj način.

203
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:24,600
 Oni imaju, svi vjeruju u te, koje kakve vračke.

204
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:30,220
 I sad, to su nama, kad smo mi došli, onda su nas učili kako se tamo trebamo ponašat.

205
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:35,720
 Ujutro prije nego izađeš iz kuće, ti moraš, izlaziš sa metlom i meteš ispred sebe.

206
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:38,900
 Ako ti je netko bacio nekakvu...

207
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:41,700
 A kao čini, kao nekakve čarolije, da, da, da.

208
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:43,860
 Onda ćeš ti to metlom očistiti.

209
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:46,520
 Kažem ja, ja to nikad neću rati.

210
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:48,000
 Ne, to se mora. Ja ne.

211
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:52,120
 Ako mene, dragi Bog, neće zaštiti to, to ga, neće ni metla.

212
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,960
 Ja u to vjerujem.

213
00:14:53,960 --> 00:15:00,400
 I sad, ali to je kod njih, to su izmislili stari, da bi mlade prisilili da,

214
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:03,100
 metu, da bude čisto oko kuće.

215
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,800
 Nema tu ništa.

216
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,760
 Metla ni može ništa učiniti.

217
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:11,400
 Ali, evo, tu su ta vjerovanja, ali svako to vjerovanje ima svoj razlog zašto.

218
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:13,280
 Kad je nekog većih dobra.

219
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:19,140
 Ali, dakle, vi ste, voda nije bila dobra, higijena, nikakvi uvjeti, ono, u toj kući.

220
00:15:19,140 --> 00:15:21,460
 Vi ste sami malariju nekoliko puta dobili.

221
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:23,360
 Pa, malariju, ne znam, nije, sto puta.

222
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,900
 Na početku su bile to teške malarije.

223
00:15:25,900 --> 00:15:30,400
 I, ono, temperaturu imaš bolove.

224
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:34,420
 Nekad budeš, imaš povraćanje, proljevi.

225
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:36,300
 Ne možeš glavu dignuti.

226
00:15:36,300 --> 00:15:43,580
 Jest, već, da si dalekati, netko nosi hranu, osjetiš mirist, ma kakvi ni blizu.

227
00:15:43,580 --> 00:15:45,700
 Onda, malo, pomalo.

228
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:50,700
 Na početku mi smo, ono, istini za volju, malo smo, premalo smo pazili na sebe.

229
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:53,440
 Mi smo se dali na rad za taj narod.

230
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,380
 Da, da im pomognete što više.

231
00:15:55,380 --> 00:16:00,580
 Da, i onda smo mi na neki način, reći ću, malo te ne zaboravili, redovito jest.

232
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:02,740
 Na brzinu nešto pojedeš.

233
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:09,700
 Onda su nas upozoravali, ti sveđenici, sestre, vi morate jest, vi morate misliti na sebe, vi ne možete non stop raditi.

234
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:14,660
 I onda, ja sam znala biti, imam malariju i sad došli su u ambulantu.

235
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:18,440
 Dovode djecu, dolaze teško bolesni, da.

236
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:18,480
 Donose sa djecom.

237
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:27,280
 Onda oni meni nekad donesu mi djete u krevet, da ja vidim, da onda potvrdim sestri što će s njim, kako će s njim.

238
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:29,660
 A nekad se digne pa dođem tamo sjednem.

239
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:30,880
 Ma, sva šta smo imali.

240
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:35,460
 Jedan put su nam, ja sam imala baš malariju, donijeli su nam, doveli su nam jednog.

241
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:38,620
 Kako su se djeca igrala i njemu su osjekli prst.

242
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:42,940
 I sad, prst je tu, malo se drži na koži.

243
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:46,200
 I ma kaže, ne bude da idu u bolnicu, to bi trebalo skinuti.

244
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:49,540
 Ne, oni ne mogu ići u bolnicu, sestrovi napravi tešto.

245
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:53,320
 Ali bojim se da će to biti još gore.

246
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,260
 Inficirat će se.

247
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:58,160
 Ja se ne držim na nogama, ja sjedim.

248
00:16:58,160 --> 00:17:00,420
 Bolesni, teško vida.

249
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:06,140
 Malo sam to očistila i onako, ja kažem, ja ću to zamotati, a morate mi doći svaki dan.

250
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:11,640
 Da ja vidim, ako no kad poplavi, morate ići u bolnicu.

251
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:14,380
 I onda se to mora skinuti, jer će otići cijela ruka.

252
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,940
 Volje skinuti jedan prst, nego cijelu ruku.

253
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:20,580
 Samo vi to napravite, oni su sigurni da će to biti dobro.

254
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:24,640
 Ja sam to tako zbilja i napravila, stavila kost, je bila presjećena.

255
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:28,260
 A ja sam stavila kost na kost, malo je bio okrenut nasranu.

256
00:17:28,260 --> 00:17:29,940
 I to se začudo primilo.

257
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:34,760
 Da, nevjerojatno.

258
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:38,520
 Kad ja poslije razmišljam, da je to neko, da je to bilo u bolnici.

259
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:41,320
 Ima ništa drugo nego osjeći, samo malo koza se drži.

260
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:48,300
 Ali to se primilo, su meni došli i rekli, evo sestra, joj on može micat prstom sve, samo je malo vidi se da je okrenut.

261
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:48,780
 Pa da.

262
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:49,920
 Bez šta, dobro.

263
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,960
 Mislim, bilo je tako teško.

264
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:57,800
 Ali eto, hvala Bogu, mi smo uz sve te nevolje.

265
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:59,420
 To je sve prošlo.

266
00:17:59,420 --> 00:18:04,960
 Ono, kad ti dođete malarija, kad ti stisne se, onda se pitaš, ma kud sam došla, jel mi to trebalo?

267
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:07,440
 I misliš, čim to prođe od veja kući?

268
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,760
 A kad prođe, ono, opet zaboraviš.

269
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:12,800
 Da, pa da, čovjek, jasno mi je to.

270
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:15,400
 To je vaš, sada je to...

271
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,000
 To je zvanje, to je poziv.

272
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:21,020
 I ti ne možeš biti sretan ako nisi tu gdje te Bog hoće.

273
00:18:21,020 --> 00:18:26,040
 Možeš ti sve drugo imati, ali ako nisi tu gdje te Bog hoće, nićeš biti sretan do kraja.

274
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:33,860
 Ali sad je doista impresivno kako ste u ovih 30 godina kuća koja je u AFAME, u ambulanta.

275
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:39,900
 kuća koja je, dakle, imate tri kuće ili imate četiri sirotište za djeto.

276
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:41,220
 Dakle, toliko od toga ste uvih 30.

277
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:45,640
 Ono što je najvažnije, imate pune kuće sestara mladih sa zvanjima.

278
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:51,540
 Pa mi imamo trenutno 36 domaćih sestara.

279
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:58,800
 I sad, recimo, nas smo tri, ali imamo šest zajednica.

280
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:04,780
 Sestre rade, imamo dvije ambulante naše gdje mi radimo.

281
00:19:04,780 --> 00:19:10,540
 Onda i sestre rade u bolnici, jedna radi u laboratoriju, dvije rade u školi.

282
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:17,540
 Onda imamo ta dva sirotišta gdje smo, mi koji smo tu radimo sve druge posle, onda još i tu.

283
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:24,780
 Da sad trebamo otvoriti jednu novu ambulantu, ne našu, nego u nekom selu.

284
00:19:24,780 --> 00:19:30,800
 Sel nam je dosta daleko, ali su nas molili da tamo dođemo raditi djece.

285
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:33,980
 To bi bila jedna ambulanta koja je isključivo za djecu.

286
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:38,760
 Sad mi trebamo urediti, opremiti tu ambulantu.

287
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:41,620
 Dobro, sestre imamo koje bi radile tu.

288
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:44,260
 Sad treba dati sve što treba.

289
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:49,340
 Opremiti ambulantu i sa svim priborom koji je potreban, sa opremom.

290
00:19:49,340 --> 00:19:51,960
 Sve što treba je, zad vam je to, ne možete vi.

291
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:57,360
 Kad smo mi došli tamo, onda smo, no i biskup je mogla lako otvoriti jednu ambulantu, sve to išlo.

292
00:19:57,740 --> 00:20:05,180
 Ali danas toga više nema, jer država mi je postavila takav zakon i one zahtjevaju to i to, ali vam ništa ne daju.

293
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:10,440
 Da, pa to je ono što smo pričali o koroni, kako se sad kao protiv korone bori.

294
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:18,320
 Svaki dan u Beninu i danas umire najmanje 15 do 20 osoba od malarije.

295
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:20,380
 Svaki dan u Beninu cijelo.

296
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:22,660
 Nitko se ne postavlja nikakvo pitanje.

297
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:25,300
 Izlječiva, bolest, može ju se vijeti.

298
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:29,900
 A sad nekakva korona koju smo izmislili, otkud?

299
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:35,180
 I sad imaju zaštite, ugraničenja, ne smiješ, ne smiješ.

300
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:43,220
 Nas su tamo maltrtirali više mjesec dana, nismo, dva mjeseca, nismo mogli izaći 500 metara iz kuće prema gradu.

301
00:20:43,220 --> 00:20:44,880
 Korona.

302
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,460
 Puna kuća, djece, siročadi.

303
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:49,100
 Da, ako vas je, da, 50 u kući.

304
00:20:49,100 --> 00:20:50,980
 Ja sam ja jedan dan se napravila.

305
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:55,020
 Pa idem, nema više kruha, nema više, nema hrane za životinje.

306
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:58,540
 Ajde, sreća, imali smo kukuru, zrižu i to, nema za životinje.

307
00:20:58,540 --> 00:21:01,580
 Pa idem, pa idem si kupit hrane, no.

308
00:21:01,580 --> 00:21:07,580
 Pa ne može, kaže mi, znate šta, meni je sve jedno, umrijet od korone ili umrijet od gladi.

309
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:09,860
 Više volim umrijet od korone.

310
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:11,680
 To ide brže, ako treba.

311
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:14,300
 A nas je 50 u kući, ja imam djecu.

312
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:17,180
 Djeca ne znaju za koronu, djeca će i jest.

313
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:17,720
 Da, da.

314
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:20,200
 Ovdje, reko jedan policaj, sma, pustite ju, nek ide.

315
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:23,160
 I tako sam prošla u grad, kupila hranu i za nas.

316
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,720
 Mislim, to izbijam, pa smiješno zvuči.

317
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:31,180
 Ja kad slušam, ono, u medijima te priče o mjerama u afričkim zemljama protiv korone,

318
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:33,580
 to je doista, izgleda kao ruganje.

319
00:21:33,580 --> 00:21:37,680
 Kada znateš da djeca od gladi umiru, od bolesti koje su izlječive,

320
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:42,900
 od proljeva, od stotinu drugih bolesti,

321
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:47,240
 od kojih ne bi se opće trebalo umirat danas u 21. stoljeću,

322
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:50,300
 a onda ti pričaju da se dezinficiraju ruke u selima

323
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:53,520
 kojima nema opće vode, niti kanalizacije, niti ičega, mislimo.

324
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:55,520
 Da, tko je to...

325
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:56,820
 A to je...

326
00:21:56,820 --> 00:21:59,500
 Cijeli van na van jedna izmišljena priča.

327
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:03,400
 Oda smo još, ono, u komunizmu, samo priča bezvezna.

328
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:06,180
 Čujte, tako se radi u Evropi, tako mi moramo raditi.

329
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:06,600
 Da, da, da.

330
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,440
 Kopirati, kopirati bez obzira...

331
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,740
 Kopija se neke stvari.

332
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:12,180
 Što se sve, ništa drugo ne može usporediti.

333
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:15,000
 Naše ljudi kažu, tako se radi u Evropi,

334
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:18,480
 pa dajte nam onda evropske plaće i evropsku hranu.

335
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,060
 Pa da.

336
00:22:19,060 --> 00:22:20,400
 Hoćemo se onda držati toga.

337
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:20,660
 Pa da.

338
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:26,880
 One, mi se borimo, idemo tamo u polje, suša, dve godine, nema kiše, normalno.

339
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:30,580
 Ljudi stiju kukuruz i na koncu ništa ne uberu.

340
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:33,240
 Pa to je ti da plaćeš.

341
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:33,880
 Pa da.

342
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:36,300
 Naša je guća tu, mi smo nešto malo posijali kod nas.

343
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:38,860
 Koliko smo posijali, ipak smo nešto ubrali.

344
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:41,540
 A ljudi nasuprot nas su posijali hektare.

345
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:43,900
 Niti jedno klipa nisu ubrali.

346
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:46,680
 Ove godine je ista stvar.

347
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,340
 Prva sezona je već propala.

348
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:50,120
 Prije onak sam ja došla iz Afrike,

349
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:52,220
 vidjela sam da je njihova sezona propala.

350
00:22:52,220 --> 00:22:54,460
 Ja sam dva puta sjela kukuruz.

351
00:22:54,460 --> 00:22:56,620
 Prvi puta ništa nije niklo,

352
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:58,260
 drugi puta je niklo vrlo malo

353
00:22:58,260 --> 00:22:59,440
 i to su tanke.

354
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:01,960
 Ne ti, od toga ništa ne može biti.

355
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:04,980
 Sam ja rekla sestrama, idemo posaditi manjoku.

356
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,680
 Možda nešto bude.

357
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:10,520
 Manjoka je, dakle, recite nam što je to manjoka.

358
00:23:10,520 --> 00:23:12,340
 Manjoka je to vam jedna biljka

359
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:13,580
 koja ima korijen dole.

360
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:15,480
 To su korijeni, znaju biti dugački, veliki.

361
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,840
 Ovisi o kvaliteti zemlje.

362
00:23:16,840 --> 00:23:19,240
 Ako je plodnija zemlja,

363
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,740
 onda ćete dobiti veće korijene,

364
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:21,540
 imate više.

365
00:23:21,540 --> 00:23:24,160
 Onda manjoka mora biti u zemlji

366
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:26,080
 od kad ju posadite do,

367
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:28,220
 kad ju vadite od prilike devet mjeseci,

368
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,600
 devet do deset mjeseci.

369
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:31,740
 Onda je zrela, ju berete,

370
00:23:31,740 --> 00:23:33,540
 čupate u stvari,

371
00:23:33,540 --> 00:23:35,420
 mora se oguli se,

372
00:23:35,420 --> 00:23:37,060
 melje se, cijedi se,

373
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,840
 da se taj škrob odvoji.

374
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:40,220
 Da, ti sam vidjela da kako radite.

375
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,120
 Da, mi to radimo,

376
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:42,940
 mi uzimamo škrob za druge stvari,

377
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:44,280
 onda ćemo i to preraditi.

378
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:45,580
 A onda to brašno,

379
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:46,620
 to što ostaje,

380
00:23:46,620 --> 00:23:47,740
 to se prži.

381
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:51,980
 i mi to spremamo na naš način,

382
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:53,140
 da se dobro upržiti,

383
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:55,500
 pomože i godinu i više,

384
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,700
 biti onako ako je dobro zatvoreno,

385
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,460
 stavljaju se u najlonske vreće,

386
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:00,120
 pa u druge,

387
00:24:00,120 --> 00:24:01,520
 tako da zrak ne ulazi.

388
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:02,920
 E kad dođe zrak,

389
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,280
 onda on gubi svoj miris

390
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:07,160
 i gubi kvalitetu,

391
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:07,880
 povlaži,

392
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,660
 onda nije to.

393
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,600
 a onda ovaj škrob što ostane,

394
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,720
 onda to opet pržimo

395
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,280
 i opet spremamo na drugi način,

396
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:14,260
 to nam je sve zajelo.

397
00:24:14,260 --> 00:24:15,600
 Vi u principu,

398
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,360
 sada u svojim,

399
00:24:17,360 --> 00:24:18,320
 vi uzgajate,

400
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:19,520
 imate životinje,

401
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:21,660
 sadite voće,

402
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:22,520
 povrće.

403
00:24:22,520 --> 00:24:23,740
 Dakle, u principu,

404
00:24:23,740 --> 00:24:25,960
 samo održivo funkcionirate,

405
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,460
 vaše zajednice,

406
00:24:27,460 --> 00:24:29,780
 ili vi onda kao grupa funkcionirate,

407
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:31,340
 de facto samo održivo,

408
00:24:31,340 --> 00:24:33,000
 da se možete za sve što možete

409
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,200
 sami svojim radom pobrinuti.

410
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:35,600
 Istina,

411
00:24:35,600 --> 00:24:37,160
 od samog početka,

412
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,160
 kad smo mi došli tamo,

413
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,740
 ili smo dvije,

414
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:39,840
 imali smo malo povrće,

415
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:40,540
 onda povremeno,

416
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:42,500
 sve smo više radili meso,

417
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:44,060
 već najmanje deset godina

418
00:24:44,060 --> 00:24:45,020
 nikad ne kupujemo.

419
00:24:45,020 --> 00:24:46,600
 Zelje,

420
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:48,880
 to povrće nismo nikad kupovali.

421
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:51,820
 I onda si brašno od manjoke,

422
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,120
 to sami isto napravimo.

423
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,300
 Ako nemamo svoju manjoku,

424
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:55,200
 kupimo korijen.

425
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,700
 I onda si pravimo to brašno,

426
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,340
 ulje od palmi,

427
00:24:59,340 --> 00:25:00,060
 crveno ulje,

428
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,160
 isto sami pravimo.

429
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:03,220
 Imamo nešto od svojih palmi,

430
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,480
 ali kupimo

431
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,780
 taj

432
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:09,000
 kako se to kaže,

433
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,440
 ni ne znam reći na hrvatske,

434
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,120
 te plodove,

435
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:11,780
 palmine.

436
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:14,160
 I onda od toga mi pravimo ulje.

437
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:15,420
 Koliko nama treba

438
00:25:15,420 --> 00:25:16,920
 za naše zajednice,

439
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,840
 za našu djecu,

440
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:18,720
 koja su s nama,

441
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,200
 to isto ne kupujemo.

442
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,460
 I onda

443
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,220
 kupujemo sol,

444
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:23,740
 šećer,

445
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,280
 rižu,

446
00:25:24,280 --> 00:25:25,320
 te stvari što sami

447
00:25:25,320 --> 00:25:26,440
 ne možemo proizvesti.

448
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,240
 ali ono što sam i vidjela

449
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:28,800
 je da u stvari

450
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:32,420
 vi cijelim tim svojim životom,

451
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,840
 s jedne strane,

452
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:36,820
 ekonomijom koju vodite,

453
00:25:36,820 --> 00:25:38,060
 u stvari podučavate

454
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:39,420
 cijelo vrijeme ljude,

455
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:41,660
 kako da oni sebe organiziraju,

456
00:25:41,660 --> 00:25:44,180
 kako da oni žive što bolje.

457
00:25:44,300 --> 00:25:44,580
 Vidite,

458
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:45,520
 mi imamo djecu.

459
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:47,260
 I djeca idu u školu,

460
00:25:47,260 --> 00:25:48,780
 sva dnaša djeca idu u školu.

461
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:50,880
 Imamo dvije kuće djecu.

462
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,360
 To je od 90,

463
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:54,260
 između 90 do 100 djece.

464
00:25:54,260 --> 00:25:55,620
 To su djeca...

465
00:25:55,620 --> 00:25:56,160
 Curice,

466
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,180
 to su curice,

467
00:25:57,180 --> 00:25:57,740
 recimo,

468
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,420
 najmanja sad kod mene

469
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,340
 ima pet godina,

470
00:26:00,340 --> 00:26:01,060
 ali ja sam ju uzela

471
00:26:01,060 --> 00:26:02,020
 sa godinu dana.

472
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:03,580
 Bez majke je,

473
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:05,160
 otac joj je praktički ostavio.

474
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:06,760
 I to su djeca koja

475
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:09,580
 su bez jednog i bez oba roditelja,

476
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:11,400
 koji nam je netko molio

477
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:12,180
 da ih primimo.

478
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:14,440
 kojem nisu obi nije mogla preuzeta.

479
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,120
 Da.

480
00:26:15,120 --> 00:26:17,540
 I sad mi radimo uglavnom,

481
00:26:17,540 --> 00:26:19,680
 ali ta djeca moraju raditi uz nas.

482
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:22,400
 Tako da su oni svi nauče

483
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:24,520
 kako danas sutra,

484
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:28,440
 kad postanu odrasle osobe,

485
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:30,360
 imaju svoj kruh na neki način,

486
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:32,540
 onda će uvijek moći nešto pored.

487
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:34,740
 Malo zelja,

488
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:36,300
 to zelje koje mi koristimo,

489
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:38,320
 to je skupo na drežnici,

490
00:26:38,320 --> 00:26:39,520
 ali onako pored,

491
00:26:39,520 --> 00:26:40,600
 kad sebi posadiš

492
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:41,580
 srednu obitelj,

493
00:26:41,860 --> 00:26:42,860
 dva, tri struka,

494
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:43,860
 ta ljuta paprika,

495
00:26:43,860 --> 00:26:45,400
 koju oni jako puno jedu.

496
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,760
 Kad se tu posadi

497
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:47,520
 za jednu obitelj,

498
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:48,520
 tri struka,

499
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:49,900
 sasvim dovoljno.

500
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:51,840
 I na taj način

501
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:52,620
 oni se uče.

502
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:55,640
 Od nas je otišla jedna djevojka

503
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,460
 za, recimo,

504
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:59,000
 na jednu farmu,

505
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,000
 da se malo nauči

506
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,560
 o poljoprivredi.

507
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:03,680
 i sad ona je tamo bila

508
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,420
 na nekakvoj praksi,

509
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:06,600
 škola, recimo,

510
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:08,320
 godinu i pol,

511
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:10,180
 do dvije godine budu

512
00:27:10,180 --> 00:27:11,640
 i sad ja sam išla

513
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,000
 u posjetu,

514
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,460
 jer ono što treba,

515
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:15,320
 što nema tamo,

516
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:15,600
 uglavno,

517
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:16,600
 mi financiramo.

518
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:20,320
 za meni je lako,

519
00:27:20,320 --> 00:27:21,360
 jer ja to sve znam.

520
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:22,340
 Da, ona je sve naučila

521
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:22,860
 kod vas.

522
00:27:22,860 --> 00:27:24,360
 Sve što oni tu radi,

523
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:25,220
 to i vi radite,

524
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:26,060
 samo što je kod njih

525
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:26,760
 puno više.

526
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:28,800
 I oni imaju puno učenika

527
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:30,040
 i onda to je njihova

528
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:30,840
 radna snaga.

529
00:27:30,840 --> 00:27:32,380
 A mi tamo radimo sve.

530
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:33,620
 Imamo svinje,

531
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,480
 imamo kokoši,

532
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:35,280
 imamo zečeve,

533
00:27:35,280 --> 00:27:37,000
 imamo patke,

534
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:39,320
 onda imamo kokoši,

535
00:27:39,320 --> 00:27:40,020
 imamo jaja,

536
00:27:40,020 --> 00:27:42,180
 od toga meso,

537
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,200
 nešto prodamo,

538
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:44,140
 jaja prodamo,

539
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:46,120
 dobar dio prodamo,

540
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:47,060
 jer imamo više

541
00:27:47,060 --> 00:27:48,060
 kokoša radi,

542
00:27:48,060 --> 00:27:48,880
 da možemo povedati,

543
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,520
 ja je u selu,

544
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:50,840
 ne ima nitko kokoša.

545
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:52,160
 I onda,

546
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,520
 svinje isto je nešto,

547
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:55,260
 mi pojedemo,

548
00:27:55,260 --> 00:27:57,180
 a dobar dio prodamo.

549
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:59,180
 Da imamo nekakvu financiju,

550
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:00,240
 nešto,

551
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:00,860
 moramo se neći...

552
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:01,600
 Samo drživost,

553
00:28:01,600 --> 00:28:04,180
 da je najekonomičnije moguće

554
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,180
 funkcionirati.

555
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:05,960
 To je moguće,

556
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,180
 da možemo živjeti,

557
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:09,800
 jer da čekaš da sve dobiješ

558
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,280
 od nekoga milostinju,

559
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:11,840
 malo ne.

560
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:13,220
 Malo će biti teže.

561
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:13,760
 Pa da,

562
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:15,320
 pa mislim i u konačnici

563
00:28:15,320 --> 00:28:16,580
 onda su ljudi motivirani,

564
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,600
 pomagat kada vidi

565
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,000
 da se ono što daruju

566
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,060
 ulaže na jedan dobar način

567
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,020
 i da svi rastu,

568
00:28:22,020 --> 00:28:23,800
 da se ljudi osamostaljuju,

569
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,700
 da...

570
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:25,700
 To je kod nas tako,

571
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:27,600
 od početka mi smo tako krenule

572
00:28:27,600 --> 00:28:30,200
 i na neki način,

573
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:32,160
 na početku malo su nas

574
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:33,180
 čudno gledali,

575
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:34,860
 pa zašto mi toliko radimo?

576
00:28:34,860 --> 00:28:36,080
 Mi kaže,

577
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,640
 zašto vi ne možete uzeti šofera,

578
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,900
 ne mogu ga platiti.

579
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,340
 To je isto i ta slika

580
00:28:40,340 --> 00:28:41,120
 nekakva bila

581
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,980
 iz kolonijalnih vremena

582
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:45,320
 o bijelim ljudima,

583
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,800
 da su to oni koji imaju šofere,

584
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:48,060
 koji ne rade.

585
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:48,720
 U stvari,

586
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,560
 vi ste donijeli jednu potpuno

587
00:28:50,560 --> 00:28:51,080
 drugu sliku,

588
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:51,720
 misjonari,

589
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,540
 onih bijelih ljudi

590
00:28:53,540 --> 00:28:54,720
 koji su s njima

591
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,780
 radi njih.

592
00:28:55,780 --> 00:28:57,980
 iz ljubavi preva njima.

593
00:28:57,980 --> 00:29:00,140
 Jer ako imate šofera,

594
00:29:00,140 --> 00:29:01,680
 morate ga platiti pošteno.

595
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,300
 Da, naravno.

596
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,140
 To nije da mu date

597
00:29:03,140 --> 00:29:04,220
 nekakvu milostinju,

598
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:06,200
 ja to sebi ne mogu dozvoliti.

599
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:06,700
 Naravno.

600
00:29:06,700 --> 00:29:07,520
 Jedan dan,

601
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,120
 koliko on čovjek gubi,

602
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:10,320
 da je sa mnom na putu

603
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:10,800
 ili to,

604
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:12,300
 tako da po tome

605
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:14,140
 drugi možda imaju šofere,

606
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:14,860
 uzmu nekoga

607
00:29:14,860 --> 00:29:15,980
 iz svoje obitelji,

608
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,180
 ti domaći sestre,

609
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:18,660
 po kojemu daju

610
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:20,000
 mrvicu.

611
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:20,380
 Pa nije,

612
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:22,240
 da mene je ni pošteno.

613
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:22,780
 Naravno.

614
00:29:22,780 --> 00:29:23,980
 Jer on ima svoji obitelj

615
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:25,760
 i to dajmo kako mu spada.

616
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:27,020
 Onaj minimum koji bu mu,

617
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:28,100
 da radi negdje

618
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,640
 u nekoj kao i državnoj službi,

619
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:30,940
 taj minimum koji bi dobio,

620
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:33,420
 kako bi mu to došlo.

621
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:33,820
 Vi ste,

622
00:29:33,820 --> 00:29:36,500
 kad govorimo o osposobljavanju

623
00:29:36,500 --> 00:29:37,880
 za život te djece,

624
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,580
 dakle,

625
00:29:38,580 --> 00:29:40,100
 mi smo imali priliku

626
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:42,380
 posjetiti jednu vašu štićenicu,

627
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:42,900
 bivšu,

628
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,040
 koja je krojačica,

629
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:44,400
 dakle,

630
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,420
 koji ste...

631
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,620
 Pa čujte,

632
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:47,660
 ima ih puno,

633
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:50,220
 koji su završili nekakav zanad,

634
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:51,920
 nekoji su završili škole.

635
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:55,140
 I neki koji su dobro učili,

636
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:56,260
 pa idu na školu,

637
00:29:56,260 --> 00:29:56,760
 pa dalje,

638
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:57,860
 to je manjina,

639
00:29:57,860 --> 00:30:00,680
 oni koji mi možemo i dalje školovat,

640
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,220
 završi fakultet i to.

641
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:03,860
 Imamo i takvih,

642
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:05,480
 imamo oni koji završavaju

643
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,980
 nekakav zanad,

644
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:09,420
 jedna djevojka koja je,

645
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:11,040
 mislim,

646
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,080
 to je tako,

647
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,280
 čudna priča,

648
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:15,120
 ali to je Boži plan.

649
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:17,200
 Kad smo mi došli na sjever gore,

650
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:20,140
 mi nismo imali u planu

651
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:21,120
 uzeti djecu.

652
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,480
 u biro kad ste došli gore.

653
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,220
 U biro kad smo došli,

654
00:30:23,220 --> 00:30:23,380
 da.

655
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,960
 Mi smo imali u planu

656
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:25,820
 uzeti djecu.

657
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:26,540
 Imali smo,

658
00:30:26,540 --> 00:30:28,620
 prvo nam je bilo bolesnici.

659
00:30:28,620 --> 00:30:30,040
 Otvoriti ambulantu,

660
00:30:30,040 --> 00:30:32,240
 osigurati besplatnu pomoć.

661
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:34,480
 nismo mi imali nikakvu ambulantu,

662
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:36,380
 mi smo živjeli u toj okrugloj kućici,

663
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:37,680
 imali smo dvije prostorije,

664
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,760
 imali smo garažu,

665
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:41,180
 ali ljudi kad su čuli sestre su tu,

666
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,840
 oni su dolazili kod nas

667
00:30:42,840 --> 00:30:44,120
 na liječenje.

668
00:30:44,120 --> 00:30:44,820
 I vidite,

669
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:45,400
 to vam je

670
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,600
 taj narod

671
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:48,020
 i sad

672
00:30:48,020 --> 00:30:49,440
 jedan razgovor.

673
00:30:49,840 --> 00:30:50,480
 došla je žena,

674
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:50,920
 pa kaže mi,

675
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,900
 ja u tom selu ima

676
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:53,240
 zličana ambulanta.

677
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,900
 Mogli ste ići tamo?

678
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:55,580
 Mislim,

679
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:56,420
 daleko vam je.

680
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,620
 Da,

681
00:30:57,620 --> 00:30:58,000
 kaže,

682
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,620
 ali ta i ta žena je bila kod vas

683
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:01,960
 i onda je dobila ljekove,

684
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:03,520
 njezino djete je dobro

685
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,280
 i onda je ona meni rekla,

686
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:06,480
 idite vi kod sistara,

687
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:08,080
 tamo ćete dobiti i ljekove,

688
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:09,320
 a imate i molitvu.

689
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:12,460
 Tako da ljudi dolazi kod sistara,

690
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:14,420
 to koliko zbog ljekova,

691
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,780
 još više radi molitve.

692
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:17,680
 Ja sestre mole za njih,

693
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,760
 to su oni sigurni.

694
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:21,140
 I onda mi nismo imali,

695
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:24,400
 opće nam je bilo u svijesti za djecu.

696
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,260
 Nemamo gdje,

697
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:26,460
 nemamo vlastiti u kuću,

698
00:31:26,460 --> 00:31:27,180
 nemamo ništa.

699
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:29,660
 Ali pojavila se tako jedna djevojka

700
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:32,760
 u selu koja je završila osnovnu školu.

701
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,660
 njih su dvije sestre

702
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:37,120
 i živi sa bakom koja je gubavka.

703
00:31:37,120 --> 00:31:38,660
 Ona ima te posljedice gube,

704
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,660
 nema sve prste,

705
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:41,140
 na nogama nima ni jednog.

706
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,360
 I tako.

707
00:31:42,360 --> 00:31:44,120
 I sad baka kaže,

708
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,180
 to je već je djevojka,

709
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,120
 obično te djevojke ostaju trudne,

710
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:47,960
 pre rano,

711
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:50,140
 ona nju ne može držati,

712
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,520
 jer zna šta će se dogoditi.

713
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:52,920
 I sad kaže mala,

714
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,120
 ona će ići u školu,

715
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:55,700
 a ona će ići u paraku,

716
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:56,880
 to je grad,

717
00:31:56,880 --> 00:32:00,300
 tražit će ona ko će nju primiti

718
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,620
 da ona ide u školu.

719
00:32:01,620 --> 00:32:03,620
 a žene u selu znaju

720
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:05,060
 ko će ju primiti.

721
00:32:05,060 --> 00:32:07,680
 I one su došli nas moliti sestro,

722
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,740
 daj primite ju,

723
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:09,600
 daj pomozite ju,

724
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,020
 samo nek ne ide u grad.

725
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:13,300
 I onda smo mi tako,

726
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:14,940
 pa nema ko ću i smijestiti.

727
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:17,720
 Onako je dvije sobe, da.

728
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:19,900
 A onda je došlo iz sela,

729
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:20,560
 ima su rekli,

730
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:21,420
 evo taj čovjek,

731
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,040
 on ima jednu sobu praznu,

732
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:24,480
 one nek budu kod vas,

733
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,980
 ali tamo nek idu samo spavat.

734
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:30,440
 Tako smo primili neki desetak djevojčica,

735
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,900
 i one su išli tamo spavat,

736
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:33,780
 i kod nas su bili lepo cijeli dana,

737
00:32:33,780 --> 00:32:34,920
 već je u deset sati,

738
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,000
 kad završe učenje.

739
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:38,580
 Onda i sestre prate tamo,

740
00:32:38,580 --> 00:32:39,160
 i vrati.

741
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,880
 Tako smo krenuli mi primati djecu,

742
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,120
 pa vidimo da je dobro.

743
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:46,100
 I sad poslije ona je završila

744
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,260
 dio srednje škole,

745
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:49,640
 pa su im je poslala u gostiteljsku.

746
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:52,880
 I ona je završila u gostiteljsku školu,

747
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:55,280
 i dan kad je ona primala diplom,

748
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:57,720
 ona je toliko plakala.

749
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,520
 Pa da.

750
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,900
 I njezina mlađa sestra,

751
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:02,320
 koja je isto već bila kod nas,

752
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:03,380
 i kaže,

753
00:33:03,380 --> 00:33:05,160
 nikad ne bi nitko mislio,

754
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,760
 da bismo mi mogli doći

755
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,740
 doći da netko od nas primi diplomu,

756
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:09,980
 da nije bilo vas.

757
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:12,420
 I u stvari tak je istina.

758
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:15,400
 Eto, tako smo mi krenuli s tom djecom,

759
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:18,740
 i puno se pomaže toj djeci,

760
00:33:18,740 --> 00:33:20,780
 i onda tako završavaju školu,

761
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:21,920
 ne, poslije se zaposlala,

762
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,820
 radila u hotelu.

763
00:33:23,820 --> 00:33:26,320
 Pa da, ima, otvaraju se opcije za budućnost.

764
00:33:26,320 --> 00:33:26,560
 Da.

765
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:28,600
 Jer oni su, ljudi su budućnost,

766
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,180
 koji idu dalje,

767
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:31,580
 koji izidu iz siromaštva,

768
00:33:31,580 --> 00:33:32,580
 koji rade sami,

769
00:33:32,580 --> 00:33:33,860
 koji rade sami za sebe.

770
00:33:33,860 --> 00:33:34,280
 Sigurno.

771
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:35,080
 Jer to je,

772
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:36,600
 više ne ovisi ni o kome,

773
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,700
 i ima takvih

774
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:39,280
 priličan broj.

775
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:40,220
 Djece.

776
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:40,960
 Mene, u birovu,

777
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:41,620
 ovo što ste rekli,

778
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:43,100
 da je ova mama rekla,

779
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:43,640
 da je došla

780
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,120
 radi ljekova

781
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:46,020
 i radi molitve,

782
00:33:46,020 --> 00:33:49,500
 meni tako odzvanja još,

783
00:33:49,500 --> 00:33:50,720
 ono, u srcu,

784
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,620
 ta jutarnja molitva,

785
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:53,320
 koju vi imate,

786
00:33:53,320 --> 00:33:55,240
 kako divno sestre pjevaju,

787
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,920
 ali i kako bubnjaju.

788
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,480
 A be,

789
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,120
 čujte,

790
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:59,180
 ne može se kod nas

791
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:00,800
 pjevat nasuho.

792
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:01,020
 Da.

793
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:03,380
 mora biti uvijek popraćeno

794
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:05,060
 sa instrumentima.

795
00:34:05,060 --> 00:34:06,740
 To su ti naši instrumenti,

796
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:08,920
 pogotovo ako je nekakav blagdan,

797
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,420
 što ja vidim ovdje,

798
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,380
 završi se i časoslov,

799
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:14,600
 10-15 minuta,

800
00:34:14,600 --> 00:34:15,360
 ovrglavi,

801
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,360
 ali kod nas je pola sata.

802
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,420
 da, da, da.

803
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:19,920
 Misli, uzmemo vrijeme,

804
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,700
 jer časoslov se pjeva.

805
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:23,380
 To su psalmi za pjevanje

806
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:24,280
 i onda,

807
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:24,960
 tako,

808
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:25,880
 svi pjevamo

809
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:27,260
 i to je,

810
00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:29,140
 ne znam,

811
00:34:29,140 --> 00:34:31,100
 nama je osobno zadovoljstvo

812
00:34:31,100 --> 00:34:32,760
 i jedna prilika

813
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,080
 na nekakav odmor.

814
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:34,820
 Da.

815
00:34:34,820 --> 00:34:36,640
 Tako da...

816
00:34:36,640 --> 00:34:38,020
 Da, molitva kao odmor,

817
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:38,440
 pa da.

818
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,980
 Imala jednu priliku,

819
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:40,700
 gore,

820
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,540
 što je bilo u Virov,

821
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:44,540
 imali smo misu,

822
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:44,920
 negdje,

823
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,640
 oko poodne

824
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:47,020
 i sad,

825
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:48,600
 taman mi sad treba početi

826
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:50,360
 i došli su sa nekim,

827
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,680
 sa djecom i to.

828
00:34:51,680 --> 00:34:52,440
 Veli se strašno,

829
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:52,980
 šta sad redim?

830
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,380
 Odi, daj im ono,

831
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:56,020
 prvo što im je sad hitno,

832
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:57,380
 vidiš temperaturu i to,

833
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:59,760
 daj djetetu prvu pomoć

834
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:01,260
 i onda im reci,

835
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:02,400
 pitaj ih,

836
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,940
 da li će sad čekat

837
00:35:03,940 --> 00:35:05,120
 da ti odeš na misu

838
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:06,460
 ili ćeš ti ostaviti misu

839
00:35:06,460 --> 00:35:07,400
 i njih ćeš liječiti.

840
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,640
 I mi je rekla,

841
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:09,700
 ne, idite vi na misu.

842
00:35:09,700 --> 00:35:12,700
 Ovo je pomolit se za moj djete.

843
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:13,800
 I idite vi na misu,

844
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,440
 najprije.

845
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:17,180
 znaju oni vrijednost molitve.

846
00:35:17,180 --> 00:35:17,480
 Da, da.

847
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:19,160
 Iako nisu vjernici,

848
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:20,360
 iako su možda muslimani,

849
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,280
 možda nisu ništa.

850
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,180
 A idite vi najprije na misu.

851
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:26,460
 To je na neki način

852
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:29,020
 iza nas svjedočanstvo

853
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,860
 koliko ti ljudi cijene

854
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,600
 tu duhovnu bogatstvo

855
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:33,680
 koje mi imamo,

856
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,840
 a čisto puto ga ne znamo cijeniti.

857
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:40,220
 Pouzdanje u Boga,

858
00:35:40,220 --> 00:35:42,760
 pouzdanje u snagu molitve.

859
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,020
 Da, svjesni smo da bez

860
00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:45,800
 te duhovne pomoći,

861
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,480
 bez molitve,

862
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:47,360
 bez zakramenata

863
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,700
 ne možemo ništa.

864
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,880
 Brzo bi se mi umorili,

865
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:50,720
 gdje ste bili,

866
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:51,700
 ne gdje što se radi,

867
00:35:51,700 --> 00:35:52,280
 ništa.

868
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,900
 Ali uz to,

869
00:35:53,900 --> 00:35:54,640
 dragi Bog,

870
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:55,240
 pomaže.

871
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:56,740
 I tako da,

872
00:35:56,740 --> 00:35:57,260
 ono,

873
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,040
 naš život

874
00:35:58,040 --> 00:35:58,840
 teče tako.

875
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:01,980
 Svaki dan je isprogramiran,

876
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,040
 bez da ga mi programiramo.

877
00:36:03,040 --> 00:36:03,740
 Da, da.

878
00:36:03,740 --> 00:36:05,020
 Ali ovo što kažete,

879
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:05,760
 to je doista,

880
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,240
 u stvari,

881
00:36:06,240 --> 00:36:07,680
 kako smo mi s vama

882
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,580
 stanovali i živjeli

883
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:12,380
 zajedno sa vamo,

884
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:13,220
 sa sestrama.

885
00:36:13,220 --> 00:36:14,120
 Dakle,

886
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:14,920
 doista ta,

887
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:15,540
 prvo,

888
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:17,340
 taj život je težak,

889
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:18,000
 objektivno,

890
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,420
 u teškim vremenskim uvjetima,

891
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,260
 vruće je,

892
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:22,740
 nemaš konfor

893
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,040
 koji si nauči ovdje sve.

894
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:24,960
 Ali,

895
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,440
 z druhe strane,

896
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,840
 stalno je radost,

897
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,500
 smijek tih sestara,

898
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,580
 veselje na večer

899
00:36:29,580 --> 00:36:30,320
 kad se sjednu,

900
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,000
 okupe,

901
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,540
 poslije molitve kad se priča.

902
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:32,760
 Dakle,

903
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,640
 to je jedna takva radost,

904
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:35,440
 toga koju kažete,

905
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:37,140
 da je nadnaravna,

906
00:36:37,140 --> 00:36:38,180
 nije naravna.

907
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:38,540
 U stvari,

908
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:41,380
 ta radost nas drži na životu.

909
00:36:41,380 --> 00:36:43,740
 I ako pogledate u Evropi,

910
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:44,660
 tu kod nas,

911
00:36:44,660 --> 00:36:47,240
 tamo gdje ima radosti,

912
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:47,940
 ima života.

913
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:49,340
 I onda umor,

914
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,380
 kad radite,

915
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,480
 umorni ste,

916
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,420
 ali ako ima radosti,

917
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,560
 pola umora je manje.

918
00:36:53,560 --> 00:36:55,660
 A ono kad je tmurno,

919
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:56,980
 svak za sebe,

920
00:36:56,980 --> 00:36:58,740
 na neki način radi

921
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,240
 i možda gunđao u sebi,

922
00:37:00,240 --> 00:37:02,340
 onda i umor duplo veći.

923
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:03,160
 I ono što,

924
00:37:03,160 --> 00:37:03,980
 ono što,

925
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:06,420
 nekako s jedne strane,

926
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:08,060
 ta radost

927
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:09,320
 i se stara vaših

928
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,400
 i općenito ljudi,

929
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,480
 kad ih čovjek susreće,

930
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,560
 tako malo imaju,

931
00:37:13,560 --> 00:37:15,900
 a imaju tu jednu pozitivan odnos,

932
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:17,100
 sreću zbog maloga,

933
00:37:17,100 --> 00:37:18,280
 zbog bilo čega,

934
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:20,820
 dobro ga raduje radost.

935
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:21,720
 Oni se raduju

936
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:22,220
 i recimo,

937
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:24,080
 na neki način,

938
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,120
 oni su zahvalni.

939
00:37:25,120 --> 00:37:27,540
 Zahvalni su Bogu,

940
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:29,560
 vjernici i nevjernici.

941
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:31,000
 Da, to je zanimljivo.

942
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:32,520
 malo uberu

943
00:37:32,520 --> 00:37:33,720
 sa svoje njive,

944
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:35,140
 onda je da su tužnje,

945
00:37:35,140 --> 00:37:36,000
 da je to malo,

946
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,080
 ali hvala Bogu

947
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:37,940
 da imamo bar tu.

948
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,880
 I to je,

949
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,100
 mislim,

950
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,380
 iza nas će stoputa

951
00:37:42,380 --> 00:37:43,160
 jedna pouka,

952
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:44,400
 kako bi,

953
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,720
 što da,

954
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:45,960
 Bog,

955
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:46,520
 to je dosta.

956
00:37:47,200 --> 00:37:50,060
 i hajde kako se živi.

957
00:37:50,060 --> 00:37:50,880
 Pa da,

958
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,660
 pronalazi se

959
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:53,820
 putevi različiti,

960
00:37:53,820 --> 00:37:54,040
 da,

961
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,160
 u tim okolnostima.

962
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,940
 Ali ono što mi je bilo isto zanimljivo

963
00:37:56,940 --> 00:37:58,100
 je da kad smo bili

964
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:59,780
 u ovoj župi

965
00:37:59,780 --> 00:38:00,320
 do,

966
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,060
 dakle,

967
00:38:01,060 --> 00:38:04,480
 do vašeg samostana,

968
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,120
 do vaše kuće,

969
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:06,960
 smo vidjeli fotografiju

970
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,040
 prvog svećenika

971
00:38:08,040 --> 00:38:10,140
 zaređenog Beninca,

972
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:10,420
 dakle,

973
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,900
 domaćeg čovjeka.

974
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:12,780
 Ali iznenadno me,

975
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,920
 to je u stvari tek,

976
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,360
 nije prošlo niti sto godina

977
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:16,860
 od kada je,

978
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,540
 to je u stvari jako nova,

979
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:19,700
 nova,

980
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:21,400
 katoličanstvo je novo

981
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,020
 u Beninu,

982
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:22,200
 je li?

983
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:22,740
 U Beninu,

984
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:25,160
 to je 150 godina.

985
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:26,480
 To vam je,

986
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,440
 to je ništa.

987
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:29,240
 Za 150 godina,

988
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:30,400
 što se može napraviti?

989
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,360
 To je dole,

990
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,140
 recimo,

991
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:32,860
 južni dio,

992
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:34,140
 150 godina.

993
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:35,500
 A gore na sjeveru

994
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:36,480
 je puno kasnije.

995
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,860
 Sjever je puno siromašniji

996
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:40,280
 i

997
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:43,680
 neće vam nitko gore ići.

998
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:44,600
 Ne želi,

999
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:44,940
 aha,

1000
00:38:45,160 --> 00:38:46,940
 neće vam nitko gore ići.

1001
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,640
 Kad smo mi išli na dogovor

1002
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,740
 sa našim biskupom

1003
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:51,320
 gore za biro,

1004
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,440
 to je dakle,

1005
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:54,480
 te grad na sjeveru gore,

1006
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:54,700
 da,

1007
00:38:54,700 --> 00:38:55,540
 i sad

1008
00:38:55,540 --> 00:38:58,060
 bila je naša poglavarica

1009
00:38:58,060 --> 00:38:59,200
 odavdje iz Hrvatske,

1010
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,980
 da vidimo,

1011
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:02,140
 još nije to bilo

1012
00:39:02,140 --> 00:39:03,200
 100% sigurno,

1013
00:39:03,200 --> 00:39:03,660
 ali da,

1014
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:04,860
 pa da vidimo,

1015
00:39:04,860 --> 00:39:06,900
 kud bi nas biskup stavio,

1016
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:07,940
 kad je već to tu,

1017
00:39:07,940 --> 00:39:08,880
 no je rekao,

1018
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,180
 dobro,

1019
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,740
 sad će on malo se raspitati,

1020
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:12,500
 ima on 3-4 mjesta,

1021
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:15,340
 koja bi ponudio sestrama,

1022
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,940
 tako,

1023
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:17,560
 sad,

1024
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:20,220
 gdje bi mi,

1025
00:39:20,220 --> 00:39:21,600
 pitao on,

1026
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,980
 i onda na koncu on kaže,

1027
00:39:22,980 --> 00:39:24,020
 da,

1028
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:26,180
 pa sve sestre,

1029
00:39:26,180 --> 00:39:27,540
 što dolaze gore,

1030
00:39:27,540 --> 00:39:29,380
 sve bi htjeli ostati u gradu.

1031
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:32,320
 Kažem ja,

1032
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:33,000
 oče biskupe,

1033
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,040
 naproti,

1034
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:35,340
 mi ne želimo ostati u gradu.

1035
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:37,680
 Eme,

1036
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:38,200
 ni glede,

1037
00:39:38,200 --> 00:39:38,660
 čudno.

1038
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:40,040
 Kažem ja,

1039
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:42,060
 nas grad uopće ne privlači,

1040
00:39:42,060 --> 00:39:44,200
 mi možemo ići na selo.

1041
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:45,060
 E, kažem,

1042
00:39:45,060 --> 00:39:45,720
 ako je tako,

1043
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:46,240
 onda je,

1044
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,380
 mi je već lakše.

1045
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,300
 Da, pa da.

1046
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:51,180
 I onda nas je odveo najprije u to selo,

1047
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,780
 gdje smo se naselili u biro,

1048
00:39:52,780 --> 00:39:54,200
 on je,

1049
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:56,620
 na veće smo nijedje razgovarali u 6 sati,

1050
00:39:56,620 --> 00:40:00,420
 i ujutro smo ona imali nekakav dogovor,

1051
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:02,260
 za 9 ili 10 sati,

1052
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:05,140
 od malih crkvica,

1053
00:40:05,140 --> 00:40:06,560
 ali crkva je bila puna,

1054
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:07,760
 svećenika nije bilo tu.

1055
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,300
 On je se dogovorio,

1056
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:10,980
 ne znam s kim,

1057
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,900
 da sestri će doći.

1058
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:13,920
 Maltene,

1059
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,140
 cijelo selo je došlo,

1060
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:16,760
 što muslimani,

1061
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:17,700
 što animisti,

1062
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:19,140
 koliko vjernika je bilo,

1063
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,280
 oni su svi došli,

1064
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,480
 jer sestre dolazi.

1065
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:24,120
 I onda smo se tu dogovarali,

1066
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:24,640
 oćemo,

1067
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:25,220
 nećemo,

1068
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:25,720
 sam rekla,

1069
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:26,640
 ako dolazimo,

1070
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,020
 oćemo naš teren.

1071
00:40:28,020 --> 00:40:30,380
 Onda nam ne prireklimo,

1072
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:30,960
 što je kupiti.

1073
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:31,300
 Sam rekla,

1074
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,180
 ja ne kupujem teren.

1075
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,080
 Ako vi nas trebate,

1076
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:35,240
 vi nama dajte zemlju.

1077
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:37,260
 A drugo vas ne tražimo,

1078
00:40:37,260 --> 00:40:37,960
 samo zemlju.

1079
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,080
 A sam rekla,

1080
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:40,900
 ima župski teren,

1081
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,820
 koji je jako velik,

1082
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:43,040
 možemo vam dati,

1083
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:43,400
 odati,

1084
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:43,920
 rekla sam,

1085
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:44,340
 neću.

1086
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:46,960
 Oći u moj vlastiti teren.

1087
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:47,760
 Što je župsko,

1088
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:48,540
 to je župsko.

1089
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:51,060
 Zemlja je prazna,

1090
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:51,560
 nima ništa.

1091
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:51,900
 No da.

1092
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:53,280
 I on srkli,

1093
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:53,940
 nema problema.

1094
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:54,720
 Za kratko vreme

1095
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:55,520
 se oni nam rekli,

1096
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:56,200
 da su nam dali,

1097
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:58,300
 imamo dva hektara zemlje,

1098
00:40:58,300 --> 00:40:59,360
 tu i tu.

1099
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,480
 To je ono gdje koje je ubiro

1100
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,180
 ugrađeni,

1101
00:41:01,180 --> 00:41:02,320
 je li to ono gdje je sad ugrađeno?

1102
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:02,960
 Sad naše,

1103
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:05,140
 sad je to puno više nego dva,

1104
00:41:05,140 --> 00:41:07,220
 sad je više od tri hektara tu.

1105
00:41:07,220 --> 00:41:10,700
 I onda smo poslije dogovarali se,

1106
00:41:10,700 --> 00:41:11,460
 pregovarali,

1107
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:11,820
 tako,

1108
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:12,100
 rekla sam,

1109
00:41:12,100 --> 00:41:13,880
 ja ne mogu graditi,

1110
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:15,860
 biti dole i graditi tu kuću,

1111
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:16,860
 a nema ni sredstava.

1112
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:18,900
 Onda je biskup nam napravio

1113
00:41:18,900 --> 00:41:19,960
 tu okruglu kuću,

1114
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,700
 što sam pričala,

1115
00:41:20,700 --> 00:41:21,660
 malo ju uredio,

1116
00:41:21,660 --> 00:41:23,100
 onda smo mi došli.

1117
00:41:23,100 --> 00:41:25,940
 Pojave ceja u BNV još uvijek ne postoji.

1118
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:27,320
 Da, da.

1119
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:27,900
 Smo došli,

1120
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:28,140
 da,

1121
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:29,200
 onda vam pokazali kuću,

1122
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:30,260
 sve su uredili,

1123
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:31,260
 čisto,

1124
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,720
 možete živjeti tu.

1125
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:33,840
 Samo obišla sve.

1126
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:37,020
 Jel vam se sviđa?

1127
00:41:37,020 --> 00:41:37,580
 Može.

1128
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,740
 Možete biti,

1129
00:41:38,740 --> 00:41:39,880
 pa možete sad doći.

1130
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,980
 Žemija može.

1131
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:44,020
 Jedna je žena bila s nama.

1132
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:45,620
 Kaže mi ja njoj,

1133
00:41:45,620 --> 00:41:46,660
 neka mi pokaže

1134
00:41:46,660 --> 00:41:47,740
 da trebam ići u WC.

1135
00:41:47,740 --> 00:41:50,460
 Že nema.

1136
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:51,560
 Epa,

1137
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:53,020
 jel mogu ja živjeti bez WC?

1138
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:53,660
 Ja ne mogu.

1139
00:41:53,660 --> 00:41:56,080
 Pa kaže uopće njima,

1140
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,460
 to ne prilo na pamet.

1141
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:00,660
 Ali zanimljivo mi je to

1142
00:42:00,660 --> 00:42:01,520
 kako ste vi u stvari,

1143
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:03,140
 koristili tu

1144
00:42:03,140 --> 00:42:04,120
 danas ono

1145
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:05,240
 svi projekti

1146
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,080
 učinkoviti

1147
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:07,700
 pomoći

1148
00:42:07,700 --> 00:42:08,880
 i razvoja

1149
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:10,620
 dakle u zemljama

1150
00:42:10,620 --> 00:42:12,520
 koje su primatelji pomoći

1151
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,840
 se temelja na tome

1152
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:14,820
 da se mora surađivati

1153
00:42:14,820 --> 00:42:15,980
 sa lokalnom zajednicom.

1154
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,300
 A vi se u stvari

1155
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:18,400
 i prije

1156
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,640
 nego su ove teorije

1157
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:20,580
 sve razrađene

1158
00:42:20,580 --> 00:42:22,180
 u stvari to primijenili

1159
00:42:22,180 --> 00:42:22,800
 i željeli

1160
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,660
 sudjelovanje

1161
00:42:23,660 --> 00:42:24,780
 lokalne zajednice

1162
00:42:24,780 --> 00:42:25,740
 da oni pokažu

1163
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:26,660
 konkretno

1164
00:42:26,660 --> 00:42:26,880
 mi,

1165
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,280
 važno nam i da vi dođete

1166
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,080
 a kasnije da vamo

1167
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,320
 u svemu drugom surađuju.

1168
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,340
 Jasno.

1169
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:34,260
 Ljudi to uče na fakultetima

1170
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:35,260
 kako se to radi

1171
00:42:35,260 --> 00:42:36,720
 a vi ste to iz života.

1172
00:42:36,720 --> 00:42:39,140
 To je tako jednostavno bilo

1173
00:42:39,140 --> 00:42:40,220
 nije meni bilo trebalo

1174
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:40,760
 da kažem reći

1175
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:41,720
 sad nemate veće.

1176
00:42:42,180 --> 00:42:43,460
 A da ja vidim kuće

1177
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:45,320
 šta bi ona meni pokazala.

1178
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:45,580
 Da.

1179
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:46,320
 Pa kažem ja

1180
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,800
 a tu je nekad bio svećenik

1181
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:48,200
 je živio,

1182
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:48,740
 francus.

1183
00:42:48,740 --> 00:42:51,200
 Recite mi kako se on služio svećenom.

1184
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:52,500
 Išao je u šumoku i drugi.

1185
00:42:52,500 --> 00:42:53,520
 Pa kažem ja

1186
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:54,420
 zamislite vi sad

1187
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:55,620
 ja ću sad tuci negdje

1188
00:42:55,620 --> 00:42:56,940
 napraviti nekakvu malu

1189
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:58,160
 ogradu

1190
00:42:58,160 --> 00:42:59,360
 od lišća, grana

1191
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:00,680
 i ja ću se ići tu prat.

1192
00:43:00,680 --> 00:43:03,400
 Da li bi to pristajalo?

1193
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,120
 Vidite ja

1194
00:43:05,120 --> 00:43:06,180
 nikad se ne zgida.

1195
00:43:06,180 --> 00:43:07,900
 Kako ću ja ići sad vani?

1196
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,720
 Pa nisam jako obična žena.

1197
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:11,360
 Pa kaže

1198
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:12,300
 imate vi pravo

1199
00:43:12,300 --> 00:43:13,820
 ali to nama nije palo na pamet.

1200
00:43:13,820 --> 00:43:15,760
 Pa da, pa onda ste ih podučili

1201
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:16,680
 naši rješenje

1202
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:17,780
 pa su i oni vidjeli.

1203
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:19,180
 Da su oni to napravili

1204
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:20,620
 i tako to

1205
00:43:20,620 --> 00:43:21,700
 dolazi se

1206
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:23,280
 vremenom se dolazi na to

1207
00:43:23,280 --> 00:43:25,400
 ali treba puno vremena.

1208
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:26,520
 Da, treba vremena

1209
00:43:26,520 --> 00:43:27,980
 i prisutnosti.

1210
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:29,320
 To je ono što vi dajete

1211
00:43:29,320 --> 00:43:29,940
 prisutnost

1212
00:43:29,940 --> 00:43:30,640
 da ste tamo

1213
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:32,720
 da živite njihovu stvarnost.

1214
00:43:32,720 --> 00:43:33,260
 Jer

1215
00:43:33,260 --> 00:43:35,980
 može se drugačije živjeti

1216
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:37,480
 i to sa svim tim sredstvima

1217
00:43:37,480 --> 00:43:38,620
 koje imate

1218
00:43:38,620 --> 00:43:39,900
 možete drugačije

1219
00:43:39,900 --> 00:43:40,800
 može biti bolje.

1220
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:42,320
 oni peru veš

1221
00:43:42,320 --> 00:43:43,680
 operu ga

1222
00:43:43,680 --> 00:43:44,580
 na rijeci

1223
00:43:44,580 --> 00:43:46,300
 u kojoj se sve radi

1224
00:43:46,300 --> 00:43:47,260
 i tu se i pije

1225
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,180
 i pere se sve.

1226
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:49,360
 I sad

1227
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:51,120
 uzmo taj veš

1228
00:43:51,120 --> 00:43:51,900
 i prostru

1229
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:52,840
 po kraj puta.

1230
00:43:53,180 --> 00:43:55,960
 po granju stavljaju.

1231
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:57,380
 Da, sad stavljaju i po granju.

1232
00:43:57,380 --> 00:43:58,580
 Da, prije nisu ni po granju.

1233
00:43:58,580 --> 00:44:00,580
 I sad mi smo došli u selo

1234
00:44:00,580 --> 00:44:01,800
 i kažem ja njima

1235
00:44:01,800 --> 00:44:03,360
 da mi stave

1236
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:04,680
 stupove

1237
00:44:04,680 --> 00:44:05,780
 pa ću nategnu štrik.

1238
00:44:05,780 --> 00:44:06,740
 Stupe će staviti,

1239
00:44:06,740 --> 00:44:07,440
 nemaju štrik.

1240
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:08,220
 imam ja.

1241
00:44:08,220 --> 00:44:10,280
 I sad oni su to sve napravili

1242
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:10,940
 i kako se mi rekla

1243
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:11,680
 vidim mi sredstvom,

1244
00:44:11,680 --> 00:44:12,600
 šta ćete vi s tim?

1245
00:44:12,600 --> 00:44:15,420
 Pa kad operem vešek,

1246
00:44:15,420 --> 00:44:16,220
 gdje ću ga staviti

1247
00:44:16,220 --> 00:44:16,960
 da se suši?

1248
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:18,180
 Pa tu ću ga objesiti.

1249
00:44:18,180 --> 00:44:19,840
 Ne mogu ga staviti dole,

1250
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:20,900
 pa biće opet prljavo.

1251
00:44:22,060 --> 00:44:23,420
 Onda su se oni sjetili

1252
00:44:23,420 --> 00:44:24,420
 kako oni rade.

1253
00:44:24,420 --> 00:44:26,240
 Onda su drugi dan,

1254
00:44:26,240 --> 00:44:28,140
 svi koji su tu bili blizu nas,

1255
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:29,880
 drugi dan nisu stavljali veš dole,

1256
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:31,440
 nego gore po granama.

1257
00:44:31,440 --> 00:44:34,320
 Pa to je taj primjerom,

1258
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:35,660
 životom s njima,

1259
00:44:35,660 --> 00:44:37,200
 im se u stvari...

1260
00:44:37,200 --> 00:44:38,160
 Na taj način

1261
00:44:38,160 --> 00:44:39,760
 idemo naprijed.

1262
00:44:39,760 --> 00:44:40,380
 I sad reći,

1263
00:44:40,380 --> 00:44:41,480
 to se ne radi tako,

1264
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:42,360
 kako ćemo?

1265
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:43,260
 Drugačije ne možemo

1266
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,500
 nego tako kako smo navikli.

1267
00:44:44,500 --> 00:44:46,620
 A kad vidim da neko može drugačije,

1268
00:44:46,620 --> 00:44:47,580
 da neko drugačije radi,

1269
00:44:47,580 --> 00:44:48,280
 onda se to ide.

1270
00:44:48,280 --> 00:44:50,820
 Ja sam, Benini predivna zemlja.

1271
00:44:50,820 --> 00:44:52,680
 Tako je lijep.

1272
00:44:52,680 --> 00:44:54,200
 Mislim, toliko je.

1273
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:55,940
 Ali ljudi su tako blagi,

1274
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:57,560
 ljubazni,

1275
00:44:57,560 --> 00:44:59,140
 nekako baš...

1276
00:44:59,140 --> 00:44:59,960
 Benini je poznat

1277
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:02,040
 po toj gostorljubivosti.

1278
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:02,280
 Da.

1279
00:45:02,280 --> 00:45:04,560
 Jer on je jedan poseban narod

1280
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:06,460
 koji prijima stranca.

1281
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,820
 I ono, na početku

1282
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:09,800
 kad smo mi došli,

1283
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:11,260
 podemo u selo

1284
00:45:11,260 --> 00:45:12,540
 posjetiti ljude,

1285
00:45:12,540 --> 00:45:13,980
 da vidimo malo.

1286
00:45:13,980 --> 00:45:15,140
 Ali ti dođeš

1287
00:45:15,140 --> 00:45:16,460
 kao tamo,

1288
00:45:16,460 --> 00:45:17,020
 kod stranac,

1289
00:45:17,020 --> 00:45:17,420
 kod njih,

1290
00:45:17,420 --> 00:45:18,420
 oni nemaju ništa,

1291
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:20,120
 ono nema solicu da ti da.

1292
00:45:20,820 --> 00:45:22,240
 on će ići negdje u selu,

1293
00:45:22,240 --> 00:45:23,320
 netko ima stolicu,

1294
00:45:23,320 --> 00:45:24,400
 ono će ići donijeti.

1295
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:26,520
 I onda znaju,

1296
00:45:26,520 --> 00:45:27,320
 već znaju,

1297
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:29,380
 toček kod nas je tamo,

1298
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,720
 vodu vam moraju dati za popit.

1299
00:45:31,720 --> 00:45:33,800
 Ne više oni znaju,

1300
00:45:33,800 --> 00:45:34,360
 na početku,

1301
00:45:34,360 --> 00:45:35,760
 da mi vodu ne smijemo piti.

1302
00:45:36,200 --> 00:45:36,660
 njihovu.

1303
00:45:36,660 --> 00:45:38,260
 Ili niste na nju navikli?

1304
00:45:38,260 --> 00:45:38,740
 Nije,

1305
00:45:38,740 --> 00:45:39,400
 nije voda,

1306
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,540
 da smo upozorili,

1307
00:45:40,540 --> 00:45:41,980
 vodu ne smijete piti.

1308
00:45:41,980 --> 00:45:42,120
 Da.

1309
00:45:42,120 --> 00:45:43,980
 I oni to znaju,

1310
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:45,040
 onda će ići tražiti

1311
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:45,940
 negdje nekoga

1312
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:46,680
 koji ima možda

1313
00:45:46,680 --> 00:45:48,060
 nekakav sok u flaši

1314
00:45:48,060 --> 00:45:48,580
 zatvoren,

1315
00:45:48,580 --> 00:45:49,700
 da donesu.

1316
00:45:49,700 --> 00:45:51,160
 I onda kad pođete u kući,

1317
00:45:51,160 --> 00:45:51,820
 oni vama moraju

1318
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:52,940
 dati nekakav poklad.

1319
00:45:52,940 --> 00:45:54,940
 Oni moraju,

1320
00:45:54,940 --> 00:45:56,660
 kokoš, pile,

1321
00:45:56,660 --> 00:45:57,520
 voće,

1322
00:45:57,520 --> 00:45:58,220
 bilo šta,

1323
00:45:58,220 --> 00:45:59,200
 sami ne jedu,

1324
00:45:59,200 --> 00:45:59,860
 sami nemaju,

1325
00:45:59,860 --> 00:46:00,520
 ali moraju vama,

1326
00:46:00,520 --> 00:46:02,000
 stranco se mora dati

1327
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:02,480
 kad pođe.

1328
00:46:02,480 --> 00:46:03,920
 Ali vi uz ovo,

1329
00:46:03,920 --> 00:46:04,160
 dakle,

1330
00:46:04,160 --> 00:46:05,040
 sami ste rekli,

1331
00:46:05,040 --> 00:46:05,860
 ambulanta,

1332
00:46:05,860 --> 00:46:08,120
 sva pomoć koju pružate njima,

1333
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:10,100
 bilo da se radi o zdravstvenoj pomoći,

1334
00:46:10,100 --> 00:46:11,260
 bilo da se radi o hrani,

1335
00:46:11,260 --> 00:46:12,060
 evo sad,

1336
00:46:12,060 --> 00:46:14,020
 u smislu otvaranja škola,

1337
00:46:14,020 --> 00:46:16,020
 to radite za sve,

1338
00:46:16,020 --> 00:46:18,260
 bez obzira jesu muslimani,

1339
00:46:18,260 --> 00:46:19,960
 animisti ili katolici.

1340
00:46:19,960 --> 00:46:23,060
 Ali kako vi svoju vjeru njima svjedočite?

1341
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:24,040
 Kako im je tumačite?

1342
00:46:24,040 --> 00:46:24,900
 To mi sad...

1343
00:46:24,900 --> 00:46:25,660
 Vidite,

1344
00:46:25,660 --> 00:46:26,720
 u stvari,

1345
00:46:26,720 --> 00:46:28,200
 mi njima ništa ne tumačimo.

1346
00:46:28,200 --> 00:46:29,920
 Oni dolaziju u ambulante,

1347
00:46:29,920 --> 00:46:31,820
 u školama radim,

1348
00:46:32,060 --> 00:46:32,880
 dade sestre,

1349
00:46:32,880 --> 00:46:35,620
 ali to se najviše radi preko ambulanta,

1350
00:46:35,620 --> 00:46:36,160
 djeca.

1351
00:46:36,160 --> 00:46:39,920
 Oni gledaju što mi radimo

1352
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:42,000
 i kako mi živimo.

1353
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:45,120
 U se na početku znali reći nama,

1354
00:46:45,120 --> 00:46:47,400
 pa kako ste mogli ostaviti

1355
00:46:47,400 --> 00:46:49,080
 to što ste vi imali

1356
00:46:49,080 --> 00:46:51,700
 i doći ovamo,

1357
00:46:51,700 --> 00:46:52,820
 biti kod nas,

1358
00:46:52,820 --> 00:46:54,360
 mi ništa ne imamo.

1359
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:55,980
 I sad i nivi nemate.

1360
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:57,220
 To su nam znali reći,

1361
00:46:57,220 --> 00:46:58,120
 pa sad i nivi nemate.

1362
00:46:58,120 --> 00:46:58,200
 Pa da, pa,

1363
00:46:58,200 --> 00:47:00,040
 logična pitanja.

1364
00:47:00,700 --> 00:47:01,320
 I sad dođe,

1365
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:01,960
 neko vas pita,

1366
00:47:01,960 --> 00:47:03,300
 pa zašto ste to ostavili?

1367
00:47:03,300 --> 00:47:04,600
 Onda im kažemo.

1368
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:06,120
 Šta?

1369
00:47:06,120 --> 00:47:07,860
 Ne ide to njima u glavu,

1370
00:47:07,860 --> 00:47:09,260
 ali s vremenom

1371
00:47:09,260 --> 00:47:11,120
 oni

1372
00:47:11,120 --> 00:47:12,600
 dolaze,

1373
00:47:12,600 --> 00:47:13,780
 počnu dolaziti,

1374
00:47:13,780 --> 00:47:15,480
 donositi njihovu djecu na misu.

1375
00:47:17,160 --> 00:47:18,360
 Oni su možda animisti.

1376
00:47:18,360 --> 00:47:20,040
 A on kaže,

1377
00:47:20,040 --> 00:47:20,700
 ja jesam.

1378
00:47:20,700 --> 00:47:23,460
 Ali moj djete nije.

1379
00:47:23,460 --> 00:47:26,200
 I ona donosi malu bebu

1380
00:47:26,200 --> 00:47:27,040
 na misu,

1381
00:47:27,040 --> 00:47:28,760
 djete mora slušat riječ Božju.

1382
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:30,760
 Evo,

1383
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:31,240
 vidite,

1384
00:47:31,240 --> 00:47:31,860
 to vam je to.

1385
00:47:31,860 --> 00:47:33,080
 I sad na taj način

1386
00:47:33,080 --> 00:47:34,400
 ljudi

1387
00:47:34,400 --> 00:47:36,380
 mijenjaju mišljenje.

1388
00:47:36,380 --> 00:47:38,020
 I puno,

1389
00:47:38,020 --> 00:47:40,520
 kad jedna žena,

1390
00:47:40,680 --> 00:47:42,740
 sin joj je imao i djeću paralizu,

1391
00:47:42,740 --> 00:47:45,520
 sad je onako bio vazdan dole na zemlji.

1392
00:47:45,520 --> 00:47:47,120
 I sad mi smo ga uzeli,

1393
00:47:47,120 --> 00:47:48,120
 odneli jednu bolnicu,

1394
00:47:48,120 --> 00:47:49,720
 da bar može sa štakama

1395
00:47:49,720 --> 00:47:51,340
 ili u kolicima,

1396
00:47:51,340 --> 00:47:53,780
 da ne plaziti cijelo vrijeme po zemlji.

1397
00:47:53,780 --> 00:47:55,080
 Mama je bila s njim,

1398
00:47:55,080 --> 00:47:56,100
 ona je bila ona prava,

1399
00:47:56,100 --> 00:47:57,760
 prava animiskinja,

1400
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:58,380
 imala je ona,

1401
00:47:58,380 --> 00:47:59,180
 to je bila kao

1402
00:47:59,180 --> 00:48:01,180
 nekakva poganska svećenica.

1403
00:48:01,180 --> 00:48:03,100
 Nekad ni bila obučena.

1404
00:48:03,100 --> 00:48:06,060
 I onda je ona,

1405
00:48:06,060 --> 00:48:09,060
 i sad je ona dok je djete to bilo u bolnici,

1406
00:48:09,060 --> 00:48:11,200
 mi smo znali par puta otić,

1407
00:48:11,200 --> 00:48:12,080
 vidjeti ih,

1408
00:48:12,080 --> 00:48:13,040
 nešta im donijet,

1409
00:48:13,040 --> 00:48:14,140
 nešta im ostavit.

1410
00:48:14,140 --> 00:48:15,600
 I onda je ona rekla,

1411
00:48:15,600 --> 00:48:16,700
 ja sam toliko godina

1412
00:48:16,700 --> 00:48:19,320
 u toj njihovoj grupi.

1413
00:48:19,320 --> 00:48:21,580
 I ja sam bila teško bolesna.

1414
00:48:21,580 --> 00:48:21,900
 I djete,

1415
00:48:21,900 --> 00:48:23,300
 nikad nitko se nije sjetio

1416
00:48:23,300 --> 00:48:24,820
 da meni nešta pruži,

1417
00:48:24,820 --> 00:48:26,220
 da mi pomogne.

1418
00:48:26,220 --> 00:48:28,620
 A ovdje sam tako dugo

1419
00:48:28,620 --> 00:48:32,160
 i nisam ne ti ono što drugi jesu.

1420
00:48:32,160 --> 00:48:33,500
 Da nije opće vjernica,

1421
00:48:33,500 --> 00:48:34,380
 nije katolkija,

1422
00:48:34,380 --> 00:48:37,080
 nije povezana s vama na taj način.

1423
00:48:37,080 --> 00:48:37,680
 I opet,

1424
00:48:38,080 --> 00:48:39,820
 svi mi izlaze u susret

1425
00:48:39,820 --> 00:48:41,160
 i svi mi tu gdje jesam,

1426
00:48:41,160 --> 00:48:42,680
 ljudi mi pomažu,

1427
00:48:42,680 --> 00:48:43,940
 iako me ne poznaju.

1428
00:48:43,940 --> 00:48:45,440
 I sestra,

1429
00:48:45,440 --> 00:48:46,500
 da nije bilo sestara,

1430
00:48:46,500 --> 00:48:48,180
 još uvijek bi moje djete plazilo po.

1431
00:48:48,180 --> 00:48:49,720
 Kaže ona,

1432
00:48:49,720 --> 00:48:51,100
 ja ću se sad obući,

1433
00:48:51,100 --> 00:48:52,260
 i doći u selo,

1434
00:48:52,260 --> 00:48:53,000
 i nek svi znaju

1435
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:54,460
 da nisam više ono što sam bila.

1436
00:48:54,460 --> 00:48:55,500
 A one su stvari

1437
00:48:55,500 --> 00:48:56,220
 ne smiju obući.

1438
00:48:57,220 --> 00:48:58,140
 Kaj što je obući?

1439
00:48:58,140 --> 00:48:59,240
 Obući?

1440
00:48:59,240 --> 00:49:00,860
 Obući gornji dio haljine.

1441
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:02,460
 A, ona nikad nije nosila.

1442
00:49:02,460 --> 00:49:03,080
 Ne, ne, to je nesmij,

1443
00:49:03,080 --> 00:49:03,940
 to je zabranjeno.

1444
00:49:03,940 --> 00:49:05,500
 I onda je ona to,

1445
00:49:05,500 --> 00:49:06,440
 nek svi znaju,

1446
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:08,480
 ja se više njih ne bojim,

1447
00:49:08,480 --> 00:49:10,420
 jer to nije ništa što smo mi imali dosad.

1448
00:49:10,960 --> 00:49:12,620
 To je na taj način,

1449
00:49:12,620 --> 00:49:13,540
 taj rad

1450
00:49:13,540 --> 00:49:15,680
 i to svjedočanstvo,

1451
00:49:15,680 --> 00:49:17,140
 puno priča ne vrijedi.

1452
00:49:17,140 --> 00:49:18,280
 Tek posle,

1453
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:19,840
 kad oni počnu se zanimat,

1454
00:49:19,840 --> 00:49:21,180
 postavljati pitanja,

1455
00:49:21,180 --> 00:49:23,020
 onda ih možete objašnjavati

1456
00:49:23,020 --> 00:49:23,880
 ono što ih zanima

1457
00:49:23,880 --> 00:49:25,300
 i reći im istinu.

1458
00:49:25,300 --> 00:49:27,520
 A ovako ići u prazno,

1459
00:49:27,520 --> 00:49:28,520
 ne smisla.

1460
00:49:28,520 --> 00:49:31,460
 Krenuli smo razgovor

1461
00:49:31,460 --> 00:49:32,440
 s Marinim obrocima.

1462
00:49:32,440 --> 00:49:35,100
 Evo sad da na neki način završimo.

1463
00:49:35,100 --> 00:49:36,980
 Za Marine obroke također

1464
00:49:36,980 --> 00:49:38,600
 mora u,

1465
00:49:38,600 --> 00:49:40,660
 kada se otvori kuhinja,

1466
00:49:40,740 --> 00:49:41,620
 mora sudjelovati

1467
00:49:41,620 --> 00:49:43,100
 i lokalna zajednica.

1468
00:49:43,100 --> 00:49:44,900
 Oni donose drva?

1469
00:49:44,900 --> 00:49:45,880
 Donose drva,

1470
00:49:45,880 --> 00:49:47,400
 vodu.

1471
00:49:47,400 --> 00:49:50,460
 Njihova je na njihovom redima voda

1472
00:49:50,460 --> 00:49:51,580
 i drva.

1473
00:49:51,580 --> 00:49:53,820
 I recimo žene koji kuhaju,

1474
00:49:53,820 --> 00:49:55,980
 nemoguće je kod nac

1475
00:49:55,980 --> 00:49:56,820
 biti volonter.

1476
00:49:56,820 --> 00:49:58,380
 Potpuno.

1477
00:49:58,380 --> 00:50:00,500
 Jer svaka ta žena

1478
00:50:00,500 --> 00:50:01,680
 mora ići u polje

1479
00:50:01,680 --> 00:50:02,400
 ili na trežnicu

1480
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:02,980
 da bi nešto

1481
00:50:02,980 --> 00:50:05,020
 privredila za ubitelj.

1482
00:50:05,020 --> 00:50:05,620
 I onda

1483
00:50:05,620 --> 00:50:07,940
 tima ženama se treba dati nešto

1484
00:50:07,940 --> 00:50:09,160
 po danu,

1485
00:50:09,160 --> 00:50:09,880
 tjednom,

1486
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:10,660
 mjesečno.

1487
00:50:10,660 --> 00:50:12,700
 a to je na njihovoj

1488
00:50:12,700 --> 00:50:15,180
 volji

1489
00:50:15,180 --> 00:50:17,120
 kako će one osigurati

1490
00:50:17,120 --> 00:50:17,820
 te žene.

1491
00:50:17,820 --> 00:50:19,140
 Kako će te žene

1492
00:50:19,140 --> 00:50:21,280
 među sobom se organizirati

1493
00:50:21,280 --> 00:50:21,720
 da dolaze.

1494
00:50:21,720 --> 00:50:22,520
 Ali vi ste,

1495
00:50:22,520 --> 00:50:23,900
 meni je toliko bilo lijepo,

1496
00:50:23,900 --> 00:50:24,500
 vi tu djecu,

1497
00:50:24,500 --> 00:50:25,920
 vi imate raspored da

1498
00:50:25,920 --> 00:50:27,220
 djeca znaju

1499
00:50:27,220 --> 00:50:28,340
 kad trebaju donijeti drva.

1500
00:50:28,340 --> 00:50:29,620
 I onda djete dolaze u školu,

1501
00:50:29,620 --> 00:50:30,940
 nosi nekoliko komada drva

1502
00:50:30,940 --> 00:50:31,980
 za kuhanje ručka.

1503
00:50:32,120 --> 00:50:34,200
 to djeca donose i to na pomažu,

1504
00:50:34,200 --> 00:50:34,580
 recimo,

1505
00:50:34,580 --> 00:50:35,060
 učitelji,

1506
00:50:35,060 --> 00:50:36,080
 direktori škole.

1507
00:50:36,640 --> 00:50:38,460
 to je njihovo i oni znaju kad djeca

1508
00:50:38,460 --> 00:50:39,680
 koliko ima drva,

1509
00:50:39,680 --> 00:50:41,200
 koliko treba donijet kad,

1510
00:50:41,200 --> 00:50:42,860
 a rijetko kad drva fale,

1511
00:50:42,860 --> 00:50:43,920
 mi moramo kupiti,

1512
00:50:43,920 --> 00:50:45,080
 onda dodati nešto.

1513
00:50:45,080 --> 00:50:48,680
 Ali redovito su to manje količine za drva,

1514
00:50:48,680 --> 00:50:50,680
 jer donose djeca,

1515
00:50:50,680 --> 00:50:51,540
 roditelji.

1516
00:50:52,100 --> 00:50:53,700
 Tako smo krenuli od početka

1517
00:50:53,700 --> 00:50:55,300
 i tako idemo dalje.

1518
00:50:55,300 --> 00:50:57,680
 Sad otvaramo petu školu,

1519
00:50:57,680 --> 00:51:00,140
 početkom u devetom mjesecu,

1520
00:51:00,140 --> 00:51:01,040
 kad posne škola,

1521
00:51:01,040 --> 00:51:03,280
 oni će imati hranu,

1522
00:51:03,280 --> 00:51:05,260
 oni osiguravaju vodu

1523
00:51:05,260 --> 00:51:08,320
 i koliko bude trebalo još,

1524
00:51:08,320 --> 00:51:09,480
 možda nešto pjeska,

1525
00:51:09,480 --> 00:51:10,600
 malo radne snage.

1526
00:51:10,600 --> 00:51:11,860
 I onda su rekli,

1527
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:14,660
 učitelji tu će aktivirati čak i djecu.

1528
00:51:14,660 --> 00:51:16,420
 Uključiti da svi,

1529
00:51:16,420 --> 00:51:18,240
 da je to njihova kutinja,

1530
00:51:18,240 --> 00:51:21,600
 da je to njihovo i da su oni doprinjeli svojim radom.

1531
00:51:21,980 --> 00:51:23,160
 Dobro, evo sjeca,

1532
00:51:23,160 --> 00:51:25,380
 puno vam hvala za ove razgovore,

1533
00:51:25,380 --> 00:51:28,780
 opet nekako sam doznala nove stvari.

1534
00:51:28,780 --> 00:51:30,840
 Hvala vama i hvala svim onima

1535
00:51:30,840 --> 00:51:33,680
 koji nam pomažu da možemo tamo raditi

1536
00:51:33,680 --> 00:51:35,740
 i nahraniti tu djecu.

1537
00:51:35,740 --> 00:51:39,520
 Ako nema ovih odavdje koji daju nešto malo,

1538
00:51:39,520 --> 00:51:40,740
 tebiško bi mi to...

1539
00:51:40,740 --> 00:51:43,600
 Dobro, bez vas se tamo ništa ne bi moglo raditi.

1540
00:51:43,600 --> 00:51:44,760
 Dakle, treba i jedno i drugo.

1541
00:51:44,760 --> 00:51:46,060
 Moramo si pružiti ruke,

1542
00:51:46,060 --> 00:51:47,360
 makar bile kako daleko,

1543
00:51:47,360 --> 00:51:49,820
 ipak se možemo dodirnuti po nekim dobrim dijelima

1544
00:51:49,820 --> 00:51:51,560
 i onda tako povezujemo se

1545
00:51:51,860 --> 00:51:52,980
 to je imao sve nekako jače,

1546
00:51:52,980 --> 00:51:56,940
 ja mislim o tome i na taj način.

1547
00:51:56,940 --> 00:51:58,400
 Dobro, hvala puno.

1548
00:51:58,400 --> 00:52:00,800
 Vele gledatelji, hvala da ste nas pratili.

1549
00:52:00,920 --> 00:52:02,420
 Pozdravljam vas do sljedećeg videa.

1550
00:52:30,920 --> 00:53:00,900
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

